description:
Ephesus was a major city in the first century AD within the Roman Empire and Paul came to this difficult place to preach the gospel. He was successful, but also he was opposed vehemently by some of the local leaders and the work suffered some setbacks. May you be inspired by his dedication to the message in this ancient city.
